  "synopsis": "A non-canon anthology of short comic stories. Its centerpiece, *Trooper*, follows an ordinary Imperial stormtrooper who silently dreads being sent first through a breached door, knowing from grim experience that the lead trooper is always the first to die, and remembers the backwater homeworld and vagrant life he left behind to enlist. Other stories in the issue include:\n\n- *Skreej*, in which Lando Calrissian, using the alias Tamtel Skreej, finds himself broke and stranded on Tatooine.\n- *Nameless*.\n- *A Wookiee Scorned!*\n- *Free Memory*.",
  "title": "Star Wars Tales #10"
